data.description:
Make this your home for the holidays! In a central location of the Dallas Ft. Worth Metroplex. Enjoy being tucked away from the hustle of the city but conveniently located to everything you need, major freeways, lakes, shopping, retail and public schools of your choice!

Offering 3 large bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, Spacious backyard that is shaded with an extended covered patio over looking the shaded backyard. Interior lot! Inside, you're greeted with gorgious engineered hardwood floors throughout, no carpet! Eat in kitchen has stainless steal appliances, built in microwave and breakfast area that opens to the backyard through the sliding glass doors. Open concept makes this home perfect for get togethers and entertaining. Located on an interior lot!

Open to traditional tenants and voucher holders.
